A zone of gratification.
This is purely theortical.
1. You learn a new skill.
2. There is stage where you have trouble on pretty much everything.
3. Eventually you learn all the required methods, functions of that skill.
4. You spend many hours (it should be easier) inflating and expanding the work that faciliate such work.
5. You may have found tediness in 4. And want to change. now you at 2 again. sometimes you might go to 1.

- Sometimes change in people, medium to use, places to do the work. May give you that surge of 4.
